nodes.text: Tekkag was a female Gormak lieutenant living on Voss during the Galactic War between the reconstituted Sith Empire and the Galactic Republic. Around 3640 BBY she resided inside Gorma-Koss in the Gormak Lands beyond Outpost Skyline, where she was attacked and killed by an Imperial.
Lieutenant Tekkag appears in Star Wars: The Old Republic during the mission "Gormak War Camps" on Voss.
